1
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:09,250
You really linger like a ghost.

2
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,040
Exactly how much money

3
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,440
do you owe out there?

4
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,360
Do you know that those people

5
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,490
want to eat me alive?

6
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,800
Spit it out.

7
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,280
This is the utmost sincerity

8
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,720
the Professor can offer.

9
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,040
Think it over.

10
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:32,980
This little money?

11
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,860
Do you take me for a beggar?

12
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,290
Not interested.

13
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,440
I'm leaving then.

14
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,400
Stop.

15
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:49,760
What?

16
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,020
Changed your mind?

17
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,560
Or are you just

18
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,079
after the money?

19
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,930
Neither.

20
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,460
Professor.

21
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:15,840
Speak.

22
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,730
I took it upon myself

23
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,090
to bring Liu Yu back.

24
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,120
Because

25
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,490
he is the only one

26
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,320
who can withstand

27
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,050
the AI information flow shock.

28
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,160
I refuse to believe

29
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,360
that a former soldier

30
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:38,740
can't overcome this difficulty.

31
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,079
AI Virtual Space.

32
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,440
11th Exploration.

33
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,120
Starting now.

34
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,970
Do I still have a chance?

35
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,339
I want you to come back.

36
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,260
Professor Wei.

37
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:29,720
No.

38
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,760
If we take it off directly,

39
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,640
he'll be trapped in the virtual space forever.

40
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,640
Then what do we do?

41
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,580
That's enough.

42
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,400
Professor.

43
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,360
I'll do it myself.

44
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:49,920
Data.

45
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,880
You may be a loser,

46
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,530
but among the participants in my experiment,

47
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:02,000
you are the only one who fits the requirements.

48
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,800
So,

49
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,040
you are a talent too.

50
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:05,960
Wait.

51
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,060
Professor Wei,

52
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,040
are you praising me

53
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,080
or mocking me?

54
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:18,920
But let me be clear.

55
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,720
For the AI's future development,

56
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,200
the exclusive commercial rights

57
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,120
must go to me.

58
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:37,640
(Thai) Entering the virtual space again so soon

59
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,800
(Thai) is too dangerous for you.

60
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,480
(Thai) I won't let you go in again.

61
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,159
(Thai) We've come this far.

62
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,820
(Thai) I don't want to give up.

63
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,610
I've told you this story

64
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,400
many times.

65
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,520
Princess Zhaoyang of the Ming Dynasty

66
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,120
traveled thousands of miles south

67
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,440
for the sake of peace

68
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,400
to marry the Prince of Siam.

69
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,840
They carried the Tears of Buluotuo,

70
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,840
a treasure capable of curing all diseases

71
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,960
at that time.

72
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,040
But sadly,

73
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,200
on the way,

74
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:12,080
they were intercepted and killed by unidentified rebels.

75
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:12,740
Since then,

76
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,080
Buluotuo's Tear

77
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,200
has been missing.

78
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,120
Some historians speculate

79
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,780
that the Prince was behind it.

80
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,200
Others suspect

81
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,480
that a conspirator interfered

82
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,880
to ruin the relationship between the two nations.

83
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,880
Thanks to major advancements in AI,

84
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:29,240
past historical data

85
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,640
has all been integrated.

86
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:33,880
AI is used to simulate the Princess's personality and memories.

87
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,080
To try to reconstruct

88
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,680
what really happened back then.

89
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,960
The Princess's persona

90
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,159
has yet to awaken,

91
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,200
because

92
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,360
the data we gave the AI to learn from

93
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,420
is far from enough.

94
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,640
So, we must take it one step at a time.

95
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:48,200
In the virtual space,

96
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:49,760
find

97
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,360
the four Bronze Frogs.

98
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,440
With the data from each Bronze Frog,

99
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,560
the AI Princess awakens a bit more.

100
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,280
And our chances of finding

101
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,720
Buluotuo's Tear

102
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,400
increase as well.

103
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,800
When you enter

104
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,800
the virtual space constructed by the AI,

105
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,160
you may experience

106
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,280
rejection at any time.

107
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:06,940
Therefore,

108
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,440
you must hide

109
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,480
your true identity as a human

110
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,800
to avoid

111
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,450
unexpected consequences.

112
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,960
I need you

113
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,240
to enter the virtual space

114
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,920
as the Prince of Siam.

115
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,440
From now on,

116
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,210
you are Princess Zhaoyang.

117
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,160
Go and complete

118
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,120
the adventure that no one has completed

119
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,280
in all these years.
